ZH: 高血压是一种常见的慢性疾病。
EN: Hypertension is a common chronic disease.
ZH: 我爸爸有高血压。
EN: My father has hypertension.
ZH: 她的高血压需要定期检查。
EN: Her hypertension requires regular check-ups.
ZH: 高血压患者应该避免食用高盐食物。
EN: Patients with hypertension should avoid high-salt foods.
ZH: 如果不控制高血压，会增加患心脏病的风险。
EN: Uncontrolled hypertension increases the risk of heart disease.
ZH: 运动可以帮助控制高血压。
EN: Exercise can help manage hypertension.
ZH: 我妈妈每天都要服用高血压药物。
EN: My mother takes hypertension medication every day.
ZH: 睡眠不足可能导致高血压。
EN: Lack of sleep may lead to hypertension.
ZH: 养成健康的饮食习惯对于控制高血压非常重要。
EN: Developing healthy eating habits is crucial for managing hypertension.
ZH: 高血压是一种静脉疾病。
EN: Hypertension is a vascular disease.
ZH: 高血压患者要定期测量血压。
EN: Patients with hypertension should measure their blood pressure regularly.
ZH: 控制体重对于高血压的防治非常重要。
EN: Controlling weight is crucial for preventing and managing hypertension.
ZH: 高血压可以引发其他健康问题。
EN: Hypertension can lead to other health issues.
ZH: 过量饮酒可能导致高血压。
EN: Excessive alcohol consumption may cause hypertension.
ZH: 高血压患者应该减少咖啡因摄入。
EN: Patients with hypertension should reduce their caffeine intake.
