EN: Both of my grandparents have hypertension.
ZH: 孕期高血压可能对胎儿健康造成影响。
EN: Pregnancy-induced hypertension may affect the baby's health.
ZH: 我们应该定期检查血压，以预防高血压。
EN: We should check our blood pressure regularly to prevent hypertension.
ZH: 高血压是血管壁张力升高的症状。
EN: Hypertension is a symptom of increased vascular wall tension.
ZH: 药物治疗是一种有效控制高血压的方法。
EN: Medication therapy is an effective way to control hypertension.
